products.name: orange
products.description:
Take a break and taste the tropics.
Our fresh and organic organges are your perfect choice sweet and juicy snack. This is an is ideal for juicing; its skin is thin and smooth, and its flesh is heavy with tangy juice.Our oranges are also ideal for eating because they have thick, easy-to-peel skins.

products.name: pear
products.description:
Take a break and taste the tropics.
Our fresh and organic pears are mildly sweet and rich in flavor pears offer crunchiness of apples yet juicy as peach and nectarine. Our pears are packed with health benefiting nutrients such as dietary fiber, anti-oxidants, and minerals which are necessary for optimum health.

products.name: bell-pepper
products.description:
Eat Healthy, be nutrition wealthy.
Our fresh and organic green bell peppers are smooth and shiny. Our green bell peppers are low in calories, and high in dietary fiber, magnesium, and vitamins C and K .

products.name: tomato
products.description:
Eat Healthy, be nutrition wealthy.
Our fresh and organic red tomatoes are hand-selected for excellent quality. Our tomatoes are perfect for salads, sandwiches, soups, pastas, and omelets, as well as many more dishes.

products.name: Belted-Galloway-Sirloin
products.description:
Belted Galloway meat is considered one of the best tasting and healthiest meats.
This is always a great choice for your next big dinner.

products.name: chicken-breast
products.description:
The chicken breast's white meat and health benefits make it the most valuable cut of chicken.
It can be cooked in a variety of ways, making it a versatile and healthy meat option.

products.name: ribeye-steak
products.description:
The Rib-eye steak's title of Prime Rib shows its meat supremacy over much of the market.
This meat is best grilled or boiled, since it allows its full flavor and soft texture to perfect its taste and quality.

products.name: sausages
products.description:
Being one of our most popular imported meats, Italian Sausage merits its praise.
Perfect for sandwiches, combining with cheese spreads, or just devouring it alone. You can never go wrong with this one.

products.name: t-bone-steak
products.description:
The T-bone steak contains a strip of the top loin and a chunk of tenderloin.
Both of these are desired cuts, and having them together creates a classic dish.

products.name: Tomahawk-Steak
products.description:
The Tomahawk steak isn't just dreamy-it's real.
It is huge, well marbled, buttery, and perfect for sharing with others. Or going caveman-style on it yourself.

products.name: bread
products.description:
A mostly baked food product prepared with dough
made of flour and water. A great addition to any meal!

products.name: chocolate-chip-cookies
products.description:
Oven baked, sweet and crunchy bites with melted
chocolate inside. A delightful way to start the day!

products.name: cinnamon-rolls
products.description:
Sweet and doughy rolls with thick buttercream icing.
Perfect for breakfast!

products.name: crab
products.description: Our Finest Crab which is fully cooked and ready to eat. Wild harvested. Legs & Claws.

products.name: lobster
products.description: Whole Cooked Lobster is perfect for those special occasions. Just defrost lobster overnight and boil for 1 minute. Sourced from and MSC certified sustainable fishery.

products.name: Mackerel
products.description: Grace Jack Mackerel - Grace Jack Mackerel brings delicious authentic flavour to your table. A Caribbean favorite, canned mackerel is perfect as a convenient meal or snack.

products.name: Kitkat
products.description: It’s the classic chocolate-lovers’ delight! KIT KAT 4-Finger Milk Chocolate Bar with the signature KIT KAT crisp wafer, enrobed in a smooth and delicious milk chocolate coating – made from NESTLÉ COCOA PLAN sustainably-sourced cocoa.

products.name: Doritos
products.description: Bite into the cheesy goodness of Doritos® Nacho Cheese flavoured tortilla chips for a tastebud-shattering crunch. With Doritos® Nacho Cheese chips every crunchy bite is packed with a burst of bold, cheesy flavour. Turn any event into a bold snacking experience!

products.name: Oreo
products.description: The world's favourite cookie. Delicious and full of Wonder for over 100 years. This traditional cookie couldn't be any simpler - rich, creamy filling between two chocolate wafers.

products.name: milk
products.description: Nothing compares to a cold glass of fresh Sealtest Milk. A light, refreshing and natural taste with immense nutritional value.

products.name: cheese
products.description: Say yes please to extra cheese at your next pizza night. Made with 100% Canadian milk, Cheese is a good source of calcium that’s high in protein, too. This family-sized 400 g block is a great way to create ooey-gooey, extra cheesy, luscious layers of lasagna, and melty masterpieces of pizza pie perfection.

products.name: butter
products.description: Butter is made from 100% canadian quality milk and contains only two ingredients: cream and a touch of salt. Good for a keto diet or to enhance the taste of your food. A must to make all kinds of outstanding recipes or simply to put on your corn on the cob!
